So, you want to create your own game. That's great. 

This chapter describes how to create a new game by using the Little Goblin plugin.
As an example I will use the reference implementation, which is currently (as of version 0.3.2)
a part of the main plugin, but should really be put into a separate application to
keep framework and individual game mechanics apart.
  
So follow along for a tour ... you can find the source code at GitHub:
"Schedim source code":https://github.com/dewarim/schedim
